/**
 *
 * @title Seratio Stake
 *
 * TODO Whitepaper https://github.com/seratio/whitepaper/blob/master/Seratio%20Enterprise%20Platform%20(29%20March%202017)%20%5Bv.%204.03%5D.pdf
